experiences.job_experience:
In SyncMe my role is
• Design and develop high-performance Flutter Web applications, enhancing user experience and responsiveness.
• Develop and maintain scalable features, updating legacy code for efficiency and reliability.
• Optimize data flow and database integration, ensuring seamless UX/UI and responsiveness.

In Pan Arab Media, I reached a professional level I had never achieved before, specializing in e-commerce projects and working with very famous brands and larger-scale projects. This can be seen through the following applications: Tiamo, Aziz, Dice, and Sahla.

In smart gate I completed numerous projects at this company, such as developing an application for clinics and a dashboard for the same application. I also worked on a restaurant management project consisting of seven applications called Ristecho and a financial services project called Cascade.

At Startup defenders, I worked on many projects, such as Sabouna and Taqneen, and acquired new skills. I worked on an application outside the Egyptian market and learned many new programming concepts. There were many challenges that my team and I successfully overcame.

education.degree: Bachelor in Computer Science and Engineering

about_me.title: I'm Mahmoud Fathi Zanoon, an experienced Flutter developer with versatile project expertise, a strong educational background, and excellent soft skills.
about_me.subtitle:
With over 3 years of hands-on experience building Flutter applications, I've successfully launched apps on both the App Store and Play Store, driving business growth and innovation. My portfolio showcases a diverse range of projects, from e-commerce solutions to service provider solutions . I'm adept at tackling projects of varying scales, from small-scale apps to complex, high-traffic platforms. This experience has equipped me to handle diverse challenges and deliver solutions that consistently meet and exceed expectations.

My strong technical foundation stems from my degree in Software Engineering (Computer Science Department, Faculty of Engineering). I have a solid grasp of software development principles and best practices, ensuring clean, efficient code. Beyond my technical skills, I'm a strong communicator and collaborator.  I thrive in team environments and excel at building positive relationships with stakeholders to ensure project success.  I'm confident in my ability to adapt to any situation and effectively collaborate with diverse teams and individuals.

capabilities.subtitle: I'm passionate about continuously expanding my skill set, driven by curiosity and a love for learning. Embracing new challenges excites me, fueling my growth and adaptability. With every opportunity, I strive to enhance my expertise and contribute more effectively.
